  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Only One of You Can Be Captain</h2><strong>I Am the Captain Now</strong> is a 3-4 player social coop game where you must work together as a pirate crew to conquer the sea. Vote for your captain in the devious council, but choose wisely cause the captain will call the shots. Which mission to take on, which path to go and who to leave behind. Being a leader is no easy task, so shape up or have your crew throw you overboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Being Captain Has Its Perks</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The world centers around you, so where you go the crew must follow<br></li><li> Double the loot<br></li><li> You get a real cool title</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/8d7eaf3bb36c41deffb00317126bdafd.poster.avif?t=1629633860\" width=600 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/8d7eaf3bb36c41deffb00317126bdafd.webm?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/8d7eaf3bb36c41deffb00317126bdafd.mp4?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't Worry Crew, Mutiny Is Never Far Away</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pact and vote off the captain<br></li><li>Complete side activities to gain extra votes<br></li><li>Or a light push into the water might be all you need</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/247a6d35608b437401fe59f018bdd6c0.poster.avif?t=1629633860\" width=600 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/247a6d35608b437401fe59f018bdd6c0.webm?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/247a6d35608b437401fe59f018bdd6c0.mp4?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every Pirate Crew Needs A Ship</h2>You are pirates so you will of course need a ship. The ship requires tight team-work to control: someone to steer, shoot, scout ahead, place planks and recover those fallen overboard<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/d74a0250239e91abea39dd295c1b930a.poster.avif?t=1629633860\" width=600 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/d74a0250239e91abea39dd295c1b930a.webm?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/d74a0250239e91abea39dd295c1b930a.mp4?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Only One of You Can Be Captain</h2><strong>I Am the Captain Now</strong> is a 3-4 player social coop game where you must work together as a pirate crew to conquer the sea. Vote for your captain in the devious council, but choose wisely cause the captain will call the shots. Which mission to take on, which path to go and who to leave behind. Being a leader is no easy task, so shape up or have your crew throw you overboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Being Captain Has Its Perks</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The world centers around you, so where you go the crew must follow<br></li><li> Double the loot<br></li><li> You get a real cool title</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/8d7eaf3bb36c41deffb00317126bdafd.poster.avif?t=1629633860\" width=600 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/8d7eaf3bb36c41deffb00317126bdafd.webm?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/8d7eaf3bb36c41deffb00317126bdafd.mp4?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't Worry Crew, Mutiny Is Never Far Away</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pact and vote off the captain<br></li><li>Complete side activities to gain extra votes<br></li><li>Or a light push into the water might be all you need</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/247a6d35608b437401fe59f018bdd6c0.poster.avif?t=1629633860\" width=600 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/247a6d35608b437401fe59f018bdd6c0.webm?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/247a6d35608b437401fe59f018bdd6c0.mp4?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every Pirate Crew Needs A Ship</h2>You are pirates so you will of course need a ship. The ship requires tight team-work to control: someone to steer, shoot, scout ahead, place planks and recover those fallen overboard<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/d74a0250239e91abea39dd295c1b930a.poster.avif?t=1629633860\" width=600 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/d74a0250239e91abea39dd295c1b930a.webm?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1482550/extras/d74a0250239e91abea39dd295c1b930a.mp4?t=1629633860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
